  "title": "1 year Contract Junior Lab Technician ($2300) #HJO",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform basic troubleshooting, in-house calibration, and validation per approved SOPs. </li>\n  <li>Coordinate advanced calibration and repairs with external vendors. </li>\n  <li>Report equipment anomalies and testing deviations to the Team Leader promptly. </li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate equipment usage and maintenance records, including SOPs, JSAs, logs, and reports. </li>\n  <li>Assist in reviewing and updating documentation and train new users on equipment and safety procedures. </li>\n  <li>Conduct root cause analysis for equipment breakdowns.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma in Science or Engineering  </li>\n  <li>Able to commence on immediate basis </li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
